title: Semantic-DARTS: Elevating Semantic Learning for Mobile Differentiable Architecture Search

abstract: Differentiable ARchitecture Search (DARTS) is a prevailing direction in automatic machine learning, but it may suffer from performance collapse and generalization issues. Recent efforts mitigate them by integrating regularization into architectural …
